  "texts": [
    "Nor-BERT small, with a precision of 0.77 and recall of 0.83, provides a good improvement with 0.82 accuracy and f1-score of 0.79.",
    "The Nor-BERT base model shows a slight improvement in precision to 0.78 while maintaining a similar recall.",
    "The highest f1-scores are observed with Nor-BERT large and nb-BERT large.",
    "These models excel at not only identifying relevant instances but also at minimizing the number of irrelevant instances that are incorrectly identified as relevant.",
    "The performance enhancement from base to larger models is predominantly a result of the differences in their sizes (number of parameters)."
  ],
